        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>expert in Perception</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You take your time searching to ensure you find everything. When <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"TiNDYUGlMmxzxBYU\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Searching</a>, you can take twice as long to search. Normally this means you Search at up to one quarter of your Speed, to a maximum of 150 feet per minute to check everything, or 75 feet per minute to check everything before you walk into it. If you do, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Perception checks to <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Seek</a>.</p>",
